</p><p>Original File name: Figure 1.  <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.rbej.com/content/8/1/56/figure/F1">http://www.rbej.com/content/8/1/56/figure/F1</a> extracted from original figure, cropped, despeckeled and size adjusted.
